{"tid":426370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★狂賀！iPhone 8 「Note7化」？全球第七爆、蘋果著手調查","createTime":"2017-10-06T14:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T10:35:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c3cbc6c606f189cf96e80e821f8dd3a4ccec7f6d","tid":426370,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:13:08.000Z","msg":"蘋果最近可說是禍不單行，除了 iPhone 8 被指銷量不佳，拖累公司股價之外，就算是已售出的 iPhone 8 都傳出因電池發漲而逼爆機殼，雖然最終未有著火爆炸，但亦令不少網友回想到上年的 Note 7 事件。<br />\n<br />\n繼台灣、日本以及香港後，最新就連加拿大、希臘都有同樣事件發生。而最新一單就發生在中國，據報事主劉先生於 10 月 3 日落單購買 iPhone 8 Plus，於 10 月 4 日收貨開箱時，iPhone 機身已被電池逼爆，螢幕、SIM 槽均被彈開，但好在未有燃燒的痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n究竟 iPhone 8 點解會出現電池發漲問題呢？暫時原因仍然未明，但普遍估計是因電池內部隔膜在組裝時受損所致。另外據韓媒報導指，曾供應 Note 7 電池的 Samsung 旗下 SDI 也是 iPhone 8 電池供應商之一，就此也有網民發表陰謀論......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news2016/20171006_iphone8_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2016%2F20171006_iphone8_02.jpg&h=98f10ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ringhk.com/news2.php?id=15790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Fnews2.php%3Fid%3D15790&d=wHzxtsvRFk5DG64ZpVbQqwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a77206ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ringhk.com/news2.php?id=15790</a>"},{"pid":"5e26306418333b40dee9fc83a3b269d8b7d0b165","tid":426370,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e32b397450a1e36005207bf0754d1277de587e","tid":426370,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:14:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而最新一單就發生在中國<